title: Miami-FSU tee it up; NW-Michigan, Cal-Utah in league games
text: > Sports Miami-FSU tee it up; NW-Michigan, Cal-Utah in league games FILE - In this Oct. 7, 2000, file photo, Florida State kicker Matt Munyon (86) reacts after missing a field goal in the final seconds that would have tied the game against Miami in Miami. New coaches, new players, new era, but the 'Canes (3-1) and 12th-ranked 'Noles (4-0) tee it up again on Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, with Florida State looking to make it five wins in a row over Miami. (AP Photo/Amy E. Conn, File)
